# ScraiBox Project State (.scbs)

## Decisions Made
- Architecture: Plugin-based, direct DI, NOT Event-Driven.
- Tech Stack: .NET 10 (Runner), WinForms GUI.
- Use-case plugins for smart context aggregation.
- Storage: Use InventoryService for file mapping to avoid full-tree scans.
- Solution Analysis: Use AdvancedRoslynService for intelligent code analysis.
- Limitations: ScraiBox should be usable in environments with limited resources (e.g. VDI) and be able to analyse new NET 10 solutions as well
- Target: ScraiBox should be able to analyse new NET 10 solutions as well older ones (incl. .NET Framework 4.8)

